column1: # The January 1926 figure is shown as an estimate and has been omitted.
# The December 1929 figure is shown in brackets on the sheet as slightly adjusted. It has been retained.
# The February 1947 figure is shown as an estimate and has been omitted.
# The October 1948 figure is shown as an estimate and has been omitted.
# The full set of 1934 readings are duplicated at the nearby Little Steeping site, by the same Engineer observer.
# It is not clear which site the 1934 readings originate from. They have been retained.
# The gauge moved 300ft south in May 1939.
# The station is still active according to MIDAS.
